longBusinessSummary: Kayne Anderson NextGen Energy & Infrastructure, Inc. is a close-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by KA Fund Advisors, LLC. It invests in public equity markets of North America. The fund primarily invests in companies in the midstream/energy sector consisting of Midstream MLPs, Midstream Companies, Other MLPs and Other Energy companies. It invests in stocks of companies across diversified market capitalizations. Kayne Anderson NextGen Energy & Infrastructure, Inc. was formed on November 24, 2010 and is domiciled in the United States.
